1: play a game with an automated human player and three bots ./deploy.sh ./runtest in different shells
2: play a game with two automated human player and two bots ./deploy.sh ./runtest2 ./runtest3 in different shells
3: view a game whit an automated player and three bots ./deploy.sh ./runtest ./runviewer in different shells
4: play a game and after a while the creator leaves ./deploy.sh ./runtest4 ./runviewer
5: play a game and after a while a non creator player leaves ./deploy.sh ./runtest2 ./runtest5 ./runviewer

